ou see someone outside with their weapon out, you MUST warn/ask them to put it away before arresting. (AOS is only accepted when they are using the gun.)</span></p><p class="ql-align-center"><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(224, 102, 102);">4.9) </span><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">Do not use someone's job to arrest them ( Arrest all thieves because they steal)</span></p><p class="ql-align-center"><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(224, 102, 102);">4.10)</span><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);"> If you die you must obey the NLR rule</span></p><p class="ql-align-center"><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(224, 102, 102);">4.11)</span><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);"> The mayor cannot put himself in dangerous situation or assist the SWAT in raids</span></p><p class="ql-align-center"><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(224, 102, 102);">4.12)</span><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);"> You can’t steal people’s weapons</span></p><p class="ql-align-center"><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(224, 102, 102);">4.13)</span><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);"> Do not randomly fine people</span></p><p class="ql-align-center"><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(224, 102, 102);">4.14)</span><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);"> Do not combat arrest (Arresting someone when you are at gunpoint)</span></p><p class="ql-align-center"><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(224, 102, 102);">4.15)</span><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);"> You can accept bribes to unarrest someone (Max is 10k)</span></p><p class="ql-align-center"><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(224, 102, 102);">4.16)</span><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);"> If there is a PD raid going on you can come back after 3 minutes after dying</span></p><p class="ql-align-center"><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(224, 102, 102);">4.17)</span><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);"> Killing other Government members is FailRP.</span></p><p class="ql-align-center"><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(224, 102, 102);">4.18)</span><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);"> Only Government jobs and Mayor are allowed to build in the PD</span></p><p class="ql-align-center"><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(224, 102, 102);">4.19)</span><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);"> A Lightsaber does not count as a weapon, unless they are using it to harm.</span></p><p class="ql-align-center"><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(224, 102, 102);">4.20)</span><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);"> Bitcoin miners are NOT illegal</span></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><h2 class="ql-align-center"><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(60, 120, 216);">Valid Arrest Reasons</strong></h2><p class="ql-align-center"><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">-Owning Printers</span></p><p class="ql-align-center"><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">-Buying/Selling guns</span></p><p class="ql-align-center"><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">-Using guns</span></p><p class="ql-align-center"><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">-Having guns on display in public</span></p><p class="ql-align-center"><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">-Selling drugs, Making Drugs, Using Drugs</span></p><p class="q