yle="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">⭐️Advertisement of non-related server content: 1 Week.</strong></p><p class="ql-align-center"><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">⭐️LTAP (Left to avoid Punishment): 1 Week.</strong></p><p class="ql-align-center"><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">⭐️Lying to Staff/Telling Staff what to do (If you find it offensive): 2 Days.</strong></p><p class="ql-align-center"><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">⭐️Threats against a player or the server (DDOS, Crashing the server):<em> </em>Permanent Ban❗️</strong></p><p class="ql-align-center"><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">⭐️Hacking: 3 Months.</strong></p><p class="ql-align-center"><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">⭐️Exploiting: 3 Months.</strong></p><p class="ql-align-center"><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">⭐️Scamming: 1 Month.</strong></p><p class="ql-align-center"><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">⭐️Using An Alt Account: Permanent Ban.</strong></p><p class="ql-align-center"><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">⭐️Trolling/Minge/No intent to RP: 1 Week.</strong></p><p class="ql-align-center"><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">⭐️All the rest (RDM, RDA, NLR, Prop Block,etc.):<em> Warning</em></strong></p><p class="ql-align-center"><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">⭐️Racism: 3 Days Ban. &amp;nbsp;</strong></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><h2 class="ql-align-center"><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(60, 120, 216);">Individual Job Rules</strong></h2><p><br></p><p class="ql-align-center"><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(224, 102, 102);">Citizen</strong></p><p class="ql-align-center"><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">-You are allowed to commit in Self Defence</span></p><p class="ql-align-center"><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">-Can Base</span></p><p class="ql-align-center"><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">-Cannot own printers</span></p><p class="ql-align-center"><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">-Must obey the laws of the government</span></p><p class="ql-align-center"><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">-Cannot Raid, Carjack, Kidnap, Mug and generally cannot commit crimes.</span></p><p><br></p><p class="ql-align-center"><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(224, 102, 102);">Cinema Owner</strong></p><p class="ql-align-center"><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">-Follow the same government as Citizen</span></p><p class="ql-align-center"><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">-Cannot Raid, Carjack, Kidnap, Mug or commit crimes</span></p><p class="ql-align-center"><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">-You must listen to requests given by visitors unless it is deemed inappropriate</span></p><p class="ql-align-center"><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">- Only you can build props in the cinema</span></p><p class="ql-align-center"><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">-You cannot print</span></p><p><br></p><p class="ql-align-center"><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(224, 102, 102);">DJ</strong></p><p class="ql-align-center"><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">-Follow the same government as Citizen</span></p><p class="ql-align-center"><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">-You are not allowed to Raid, Kidnap, Mug or commit crimes</span></p><p class="ql-align-center"><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">- You are allowed to build a base but must be publicly accessible</span></p><p class="ql-align-center"><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">-You cannot print</span></p><p class="ql-align-center"><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">-You can build Radios and DJ controllers outside but not on the road</span></p><p><br></p><p class="ql-align-center"><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(224, 102, 102);">Gun dealer</strong></p><p class="ql-align-center"><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">-Follows same government rules as Citizen</span></p><p class="ql-align-center"><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">-It will be classified as a crime if you are caught supplying in public</span></p><p class="ql-align-center"><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">-Has to make a gun shop in public and cannot base with the good and bad</span></p><p class="ql-align-center"><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">-You are allowed to print</span></p><p class="ql-align-center"><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">-IMPORTANT: Self Supply as a Gun Dealer with large arms can result in a warn</span></p><p><br></p><p class="ql-align-center"><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(224, 102, 102);">Hobo</strong></p><p class="ql-align-center"><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">-Follows same government rules as citizen, yet cannot base in buildings or own a car while you are still a Hobo</span></p><p class="ql-align-center"><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(153, 153, 15