);">-Unrestricted on Gun Laws</span></p><p><br></p><h2 class="ql-align-center"><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(60, 120, 216);">The Good (If you side with The Bad, it will be classified as FailRP)</strong></h2><p class="ql-align-center"><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(224, 102, 102);">Bank Guard</strong></p><p class="ql-align-center"><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">-Protects the Banker and his Bank from unwanted people</span></p><p class="ql-align-center"><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">-Is devoted to the law, and if caught breaking it, will result in a FailRP</span></p><p class="ql-align-center"><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">-Cannot Print, Mug, Kidnap, raid or Carjack</span></p><p class="ql-align-center"><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">-Must Base with the Banker if available</span></p><p class="ql-align-center"><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">-Follows the same gun laws as Citizen</span></p><p><br></p><p class="ql-align-center"><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(224, 102, 102);">Banker</strong></p><p class="ql-align-center"><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">-Follows the same government as Citizen</span></p><p class="ql-align-center"><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">-Can base in bank / Normal house while posing it as a secure building</span></p><p class="ql-align-center"><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">-They alert the Police to Bank robberies, and do their best to secure the Bank pre-attack</span></p><p class="ql-align-center"><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(153, 153, 153);">-Assistance in the main Bank robbery will result in FailRP</span></p><p class="ql-align-